* OPS4J repositories

  Snapshots of the Pax Plugin are regularly deployed to the OPS4J snapshot repository:

+---+
  <pluginRepositories>
    <pluginRepository>
      <id>ops4j-snapshots</id>
      <url>http://repository.ops4j.org/mvn-snapshots</url>
      <releases>
        <enabled>false</enabled>
      </releases>
    </pluginRepository>
  </pluginRepositories>
+---+

  Releases are deployed to the main OPS4J repository and announced on the {{{http://wiki.ops4j.org}OPS4J wiki}}:

+---+
  <pluginRepositories>
    <pluginRepository>
      <id>ops4j-standard</id>
      <url>http://repository.ops4j.org/maven2</url>
      <snapshots>
        <enabled>false</enabled>
      </snapshots>
    </pluginRepository>
  </pluginRepositories>
+---+

